---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Icon from "../components/Icon.jsx";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="FAQ"
  description="Frequently asked questions about tattoos, piercings, and appointments."
>
  <section class="section-block">
    <div class="section-header">
      <span class="section-label">FAQ</span>
      <div>
        <h1 class="section-heading">Answers before you book</h1>
        <p class="section-subhead">
          Everything you need to know about scheduling, pricing, safety, and
          caring for your new tattoo or piercing. Call us if you don’t see your
          question below—we’re happy to help.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-grid">
      <article class="luxe-card faq-section">
        <header class="faq-section__header">
          <Icon
            id="faq-booking"
            src="/icons/schedule_24dp.svg"
            className="faq-icon"
            title="Booking & Appointments"
          />
          <h2>Booking &amp; appointments</h2>
        </header>
        <dl class="faq-list">
          <div>
            <dt>How do I book?</dt>
            <dd>
              Call <a href="tel:+13172867092">(317) 286-7092</a>, submit the <a
                href="/contact">contact form</a
              >, or stop by the studio during business hours. We’ll gather
              details and secure your time slot.
            </dd>
          </div>
          <div>
            <dt>Do you take walk-ins?</dt>
            <dd>
              Yes—piercing walk-ins are welcome daily and tattoo walk-ins are
              offered when artists have availability. Call ahead if you want to
              confirm before you drive over.
            </dd>
          </div>
          <div>
            <dt>What’s the cancellation policy?</dt>
            <dd>
              Please give us 24 hours’ notice so we can refill the slot.
              Same-day cancellations or no-shows may forfeit deposits.
            </dd>
          </div>
          <div>
            <dt>Is a deposit required?</dt>
            <dd>
              Yes—deposits vary by project size and are applied to your final
              total. We’ll quote the amount when we book.
            </dd>
          </div>
        </dl>
      </article>

      <article class="luxe-card faq-section">
        <header class="faq-section__header">
          <Icon
            id="faq-pricing"
            src="/icons/payments_24dp.svg"
            className="faq-icon"
            title="Pricing"
          />
          <h2>Pricing</h2>
        </header>
        <dl class="faq-list">
          <div>
            <dt>How much do tattoos cost?</dt>
            <dd>
              Mini pieces start around $80. Larger or custom designs are quoted
              during consults and typically priced by the hour.
            </dd>
          </div>
          <div>
            <dt>What payments are accepted?</dt>
            <dd>
              We accept cash, debit, and major credit cards. Cash is appreciated
              for multi-hour sessions and may qualify for a discount.
            </dd>
          </div>
          <div>
            <dt>Do you offer payment plans?</dt>
            <dd>
              We don’t offer financing, but we can split extensive projects into
              multiple sessions to spread out costs.
            </dd>
          </div>
        </dl>
      </article>

      <article class="luxe-card faq-section">
        <header class="faq-section__header">
          <Icon
            id="faq-age"
            src="/icons/fiber_new_24dp.svg"
            className="faq-icon"
            title="Age and ID Requirements"
          />
          <h2>Age &amp; ID requirements</h2>
        </header>
        <dl class="faq-list">
          <div>
            <dt>Minimum age for tattoos?</dt>
            <dd>
              Guests must be 18+ with valid government-issued photo ID—no
              exceptions. That includes driver’s license, passport, or state ID.
            </dd>
          </div>
          <div>
            <dt>Can minors get piercings?</dt>
            <dd>
              Selected piercings are available for ages 16–17 with
              parent/guardian present. Both parties must bring ID. Some
              placements require 18+.
            </dd>
          </div>
          <div>
            <dt>Forgot my ID—now what?</dt>
            <dd>
              We can’t proceed without legal ID. Please reschedule and bring
              valid identification so we stay compliant with Indiana
              regulations.
            </dd>
          </div>
        </dl>
      </article>

      <article class="luxe-card faq-section">
        <header class="faq-section__header">
          <Icon
            id="faq-health"
            src="/icons/healing_24dp.svg"
            className="faq-icon"
            title="Health and Safety"
          />
          <h2>Health &amp; safety</h2>
        </header>
        <dl class="faq-list">
          <div>
            <dt>Are you licensed and inspected?</dt>
            <dd>
              Absolutely. Catharsis Body Art is licensed through the Hendricks
              County Health Department and every artist maintains bloodborne
              pathogen certification.
            </dd>
          </div>
          <div>
            <dt>What protocols do you follow?</dt>
            <dd>
              Single-use needles, disposable cartridges, medical-grade
              sterilization, barrier film on all touch points, and full
              disinfection between clients.
            </dd>
          </div>
          <div>
            <dt>Pregnant or nursing?</dt>
            <dd>
              We recommend postponing tattoos and piercings until after
              pregnancy and nursing. Consult your healthcare provider if unsure.
            </dd>
          </div>
        </dl>
      </article>

      <article class="luxe-card faq-section">
        <header class="faq-section__header">
          <Icon
            id="faq-aftercare"
            src="/icons/healing_24dp.svg"
            className="faq-icon"
            title="Aftercare"
          />
          <h2>Aftercare</h2>
        </header>
        <dl class="faq-list">
          <div>
            <dt>Healing timelines?</dt>
            <dd>
              Surface healing is 2–3 weeks; complete healing can take up to 3
              months. Follow our <a href="/aftercare">aftercare guide</a> for the
              best outcome.
            </dd>
          </div>
          <div>
            <dt>Issues with my tattoo?</dt>
            <dd>
              Contact us immediately if you see unusual redness, swelling, or
              irritation. We include complimentary touch-ups within 3 months for
              normal wear.
            </dd>
          </div>
          <div>
            <dt>When can I swim or work out?</dt>
            <dd>
              Wait 2–3 weeks before swimming, hot tubs, or high-intensity
              workouts. Light exercise is usually fine after the first week.
            </dd>
          </div>
        </dl>
      </article>

      <article class="luxe-card faq-section">
        <header class="faq-section__header">
          <Icon
            id="faq-general"
            src="/icons/info_24dp.svg"
            className="faq-icon"
            title="General Questions"
          />
          <h2>General</h2>
        </header>
        <dl class="faq-list">
          <div>
            <dt>Do you do cover-ups?</dt>
            <dd>
              Yes—bring reference photos and we’ll map a design that obscures
              the original piece effectively.
            </dd>
          </div>
          <div>
            <dt>Can I bring a friend?</dt>
            <dd>
              One guest is welcome. Additional friends may need to wait in the
              lounge depending on space.
            </dd>
          </div>
          <div>
            <dt>Consultations?</dt>
            <dd>
              Complimentary for custom work. We’ll review placement, size,
              pricing, and schedule your session.
            </dd>
          </div>
          <div>
            <dt>Second thoughts on my design?</dt>
            <dd>
              No rush—let’s only proceed when you’re confident. We’re happy to
              iterate or pause until you’re ready.
            </dd>
          </div>
        </dl>
      </article>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-footer">
      <h2>Need something specific?</h2>
      <p>
        Reach out for personalized recommendations, jewelry sizing questions, or
        to talk through a custom concept. We answer messages within one business
        day.
      </p>
      <div class="faq-footer__actions">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn-cta">Contact us</a>
        <a href="tel:+13172867092" class="btn-outline">Call (317) 286-7092</a>
        <a href="/aftercare" class="btn-outline">View aftercare</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
